30 'Sec. B-2. 35-A MRSA §302, sub-§1-A, ¶D-1 is enacted to read:
31 D-1. "Investor relations" means an activity, communication, service or expense for the
32 purpose of promoting, supporting or managing a public utility's relationship with
33 current or potential investors, shareholders, securities analysts, investment advisors or
34 financial media or for the purpose of marketing to enhance the public utility's stock
35 price, market perception or investment appeal.'
